        "custom_liquid": "<!--\n  Magic Perfume DE — Vergleichs-Advertorial (Blind-Test) — paste-ready for Shopify Custom Liquid.\n\n  USAGE:\n  1. Online Store → Themes → Customize → open the target page.\n  2. Add section → Custom Liquid → paste this entire file.\n  3. Save. Optionally add shopify-hide-chrome.liquid as a second Custom Liquid\n     section at the very top to hide header/footer/announcement on this page.\n\n  All CSS is scoped under `.mp-vergleich` — no collisions with theme styles.\n  Images load from the Shopify CDN (already uploaded). No Liquid tags inside.\n-->\n\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n<style>\n  .mp-vergleich, .mp-vergleich *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}\n  .mp-vergleich{font-family:'Inter',system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;color:#2b2b2b;background:#fff;font-size:18px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.7}\n  .mp-vergleich p{margin-bottom:22px}\n  .mp-vergleich strong{color:#1a1a1a}\n  .mp-vergleich a{color:#1e3a5f}\n\n  .mp-vergleich .wrap{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}\n\n  /* Eyebrow */\n  .mp-vergleich .eyebrow{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.6px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1e3a5f}\n\n  /* Review Header */\n  .mp-vergleich .review-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 0 0}\n  .mp-vergleich .review-head .pub{font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:14px}\n  .mp-vergleich .review-head .date{color:#9a9a9a;font-size:14px}\n\n  /* Hero */\n  .mp-vergleich h1{font-size:40px;font-weight:800;line-height:1.18;letter-spacing:-0.8px;color:#1a1a1a;margin:18px 0 16px}\n  .mp-vergleich .standfirst{font-size:20px;font-weight:400;color:#6e6e6e;margin-bottom:30px;line-height:1.5}\n  .mp-vergleich .byline{font-size:13px;color:#6e6e6e;margin-bottom:24px}\n  .mp-vergleich .byline strong{color:#1a1a1a;font-weight:700}\n\n  .mp-vergleich figure{margin:30px 0}\n  .mp-vergleich figure img{width:100%;height:auto;display:block;border-radius:6px}\n\n  /* Divider */\n  .mp-vergleich hr{border:none;border-top:1px solid #e7e7e7;margin:36px 0}\n\n  /* Highlight box */\n  .mp-vergleich .callout{background:#f6f7f9;border-radius:10px;padding:28px 28px;margin:28px 0;font-size:17px;line-height:1.7}\n  .mp-vergleich .callout strong{color:#1a1a1a}\n\n  /* Section headings */\n  .mp-vergleich h2{font-size:30px;font-weight:800;line-height:1.25;letter-spacing:-0.5px;color:#1a1a1a;margin:46px 0 18px}\n\n  /* Criteria / Checks */\n  .mp-vergleich .checks{margin:18px 0 8px}\n  .mp-vergleich .check{padding:26px 0;border-top:1px solid #e7e7e7}\n  .mp-vergleich .check:last-child{border-bottom:1px solid #e7e7e7}\n  .mp-vergleich .check .num{font-size:30px;font-weight:800;color:#1e3a5f;line-height:1;display:inline-block;vertical-align:baseline;margin-right:14px;margin-bottom:10px}\n  .mp-vergleich .check h3{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;display:inline-block;vertical-align:baseline;margin-bottom:10px}\n  .mp-vergleich .check p{font-size:16px;color:#6e6e6e;margin-bottom:0}\n\n  /* Trust bar */\n  .mp-vergleich .trust{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:36px;flex-wrap:wrap;text-align:center;padding:30px 0;border-top:1px solid #e7e7e7;border-bottom:1px solid #e7e7e7;margin:36px 0}\n  .mp-vergleich .trust .num{font-size:25px;font-weight:800;color:#1e3a5f}\n  .mp-vergleich .trust .lab{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.8px;color:#6e6e6e;margin-top:3px}\n\n  /* Comparison Table */\n  .mp-vergleich .h2h{width:100%;overflow-x:auto;margin:28px 0}\n  .mp-vergleich .h2h table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13.5px}\n  .mp-vergleich .h2h th{border-bottom:2px solid #1a1a1a;padding:11px 12px;text-align:left;font-weight:700;white-space:nowrap;font-size:12px;text-transform:upper